[{"tag_name":"1.0-nx","name":"The Legend of Sword and Fairy - Switch port 1.0-nx","body":"## Installation:\r\n\r\n- Download the official PC game freeware (for Windows 98): http://update1.baiyou100.com/resource/Pal98rqp.zip\r\n- Create `/switch/sdlpal` folder and copy into it:\r\n  - `sdlpal.nro`\r\n  - `sdlpal.cfg`\r\n  - All data files\r\n- If needed:\r\n  - Download the english patch: http://www.romhacking.net/translations/2441/\r\n  - Overwrite `M.msg`, `Sss.mkf` and `Word.dat` + copy `m_chs.slf` and `m_eng.slf` from the *win_files* folder of the archive to `/switch/sdlpal`.\r\n\r\nNote: [RetroArch GLSL Shaders](https://github.com/libretro/glsl-shaders) are supported. To enable them:\r\n - Set `EnableGLSL` option to `1` in `sdlpal.cfg`\r\n - Set `Shader` option with the name of your shader (ex: `Shader=4xbrz.glsl`)\r\n - Copy the shader into `/switch/sdlpal`\r\n\r\n## Controls:\r\n\r\n| Keys | Exploration | Combat mode |\r\n| --- | --- | --- |\r\n| Up | Move to North / Up | Up  |\r\n| Down | Move to South / Down | Down  |\r\n| Left | Move to West / Left | Left  |\r\n| Right | Move to East / Right | Right |\r\n| A | Select / Interact / Skip dialogues | Select |\r\n| Y | Spell | Attack |\r\n| B | Open menu / Cancel | Cancel |\r\n| X | Status | Status |\r\n| Hold L + Up | Jump to the previous page of \"Item\" | Jump to the previous page of \"Item\" |\r\n| Hold L + Down | Jump to the next page of \"Item\" | Jump to the next page of \"Item\" |\r\n| Hold L + Left | Jump to the first \"Item\" of current page | Jump to the first \"Item\" of current page |\r\n| Hold L + Right | Jump to the last \"Item\" of current page | Jump to the last \"Item\" of current page |\r\n| Hold L + A | - | Defend |\r\n| Hold L + Y | - | Auto mode (COOP) |\r\n| Hold L + B | Leave game (with confirmation) | Flee |\r\n| Hold L + X | - | Repeat |\r\n| R | Use Item | Use Item |\r\n| Hold L + R | Equip Item | Throw Item |\r\n\r\n\r\n## Changelog:\r\n\r\n1.0-nx:\r\n- First public release\r\n","asse